
---

# 🧹 **.gitignore (Node + Python + Expo + Windows)**

```gitignore
# Node
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-error.log
dist/
build/

# Expo / React Native
.expo/
.expo-shared/
*.log
*.tmp
*.keystore
*.jks
*.p8
*.p12
*.key
*.mobileprovision

# Metro bundler cache
.expo/
.expo-shared/
.expo/web-build/
.expo/web-cache/

# iOS
ios/Pods/
ios/build/
*.xcworkspace
*.xcuserdata/
*.xcuserstate

# Android
android/.gradle/
android/.idea/
android/local.properties
android/app/build/

# Python
venv/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
*.egg-info/
.env

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Environment files
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

# Logs
logs/
*.log

# Temporary
tmp/
temp/
